      <div class="wwf-phs-content-left ">
        <div class="wwf-phs-border ">
          <h1>New hope for African rhinos</h1>
          <p><p>In September 2023, the IUCN announced that although poaching remains a threat, African rhino populations (both black and white rhinos) are increasing.</p></p>


          

          <div class="btn-wrap">
                
     
     
     
      
     </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="wwf-phs-content">
                  <div class="wwf-phs-content" style="background-image: url(https://www.wwf.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/hero_m/public/2023-11/_WW188625%20%281%29.jpg?h=3e43625b&amp;itok=0Hajtu0S);">
                        <div style="height: 3rem;" class="copyright--image">© Martin Harvey / WWF</div>
                      </div>
              </div>
    </div>
  </div>
        <nav id="js-page-nav" class="page_nav">
      <div class="content">
                  <a class="anchor_link " href="#issue" ga-on="click" ga-event-category="CTAButton" ga-event-action="click - #issue" ga-event-label=" New hope for African rhinos  Issue">Issue</a>
                  <a class="anchor_link " href="#solution" ga-on="click" ga-event-category="CTAButton" ga-event-action="click - #solution" ga-event-label=" New hope for African rhinos  Solution and Result">Solution and Result</a>
                          <span class="btn share_container" onclick="">
          <a target="_blank" href="https://www.twitter.com/share?url=https://www.wwf.org.uk/success-stories/new-hope-african-rhinos&text=New hope for African rhinos"><i class="fa-brands fa-x-twitter"></i></a>
